# ── NordStern monorepo — root ignore ────────────────────────────────────────
# Shared safety net for the whole repo. Per-app .gitignore files still apply and
# win locally; this file exists so generated output and machine-specific files
# can never leak into version control again (see R6 M1).

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Build output / generated
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/.turbo/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# Test / coverage
**/coverage/

# Caches
**/.cache/

# Secrets & local env — never commit; templates (*.env.example) stay tracked
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!**/.env.example

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Machine-specific / editor / shell junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.zshrc
.bashrc
.zsh_history
.bash_history
